@startuml Auth & Profile Flow

actor User
participant "LoginView" as Login
participant "ProfileView" as Profile
database "sessionStorage" as Storage
participant "Backend API" as API

== Logowanie ==
User -> Login: Podaje e-mail i hasło
Login -> API: POST /api/Users/login
API --> Login: 200 OK (AccessToken, UserData)
Login -> Storage: Zapisz token, userName, userId
Login -> Profile: Przekierowanie (Router push)

== Ładowanie Profilu ==
Profile -> Storage: Pobierz token i userId
Profile -> API: GET /api/Users/profile/{id} (Header: Bearer token)
API --> Profile: Dane profilu (DisplayName, Bio, Stats)

Profile -> API: GET /api/Pins/user/{id}
API --> Profile: Lista pinów użytkownika

== Zmiana Awatara ==
User -> Profile: Wybiera plik i zatwierdza
Profile -> API: POST /profile/{id}/avatar (FormData)
API --> Profile: 200 OK
Profile -> Profile: Odśwież dane (fetchData)

@enduml